lead_paragraph: With the vote count nearly completed, the pro-Western Georgian Dream party, led by Prime Minister Giorgi Kvirikashvili, held a wide lead over its rival.

headline.print_headline: Georgia Election Keeps the Governing Party in Control
headline.main: Georgia’s Governing Party Is Victorious in Parliamentary Election
